{"tid":683594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曹星如眼角腫左8個月都未好返 施斯斷腳6個月康復","createTime":"2018-05-29T23:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T14:10:28.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa1815b02d018caef3bc6f5638671c7c8b1675a","tid":683594,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:22:07.000Z","msg":"2006年6月7日，施斯代表法國出戰世界盃前的最後一場熱身賽，當時的對手是中國。開賽僅10分鐘，中國中場鄭智與施斯「埋身肉搏」，卻意外地將施斯的右腳踢成兩截。施斯因此錯過了2006年德國世界盃，<span style=\"color: red;\">並於6個半月康復。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩咩，井上升磅，個拳王位要排名第1,2爭奪<br />\n打排十幾等退休既河野都要比人當沙包打會<br />\n<br />\n唔怕比排第二名既賓仔打死咩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e070bd72d3801992a370c1e10893fed86eafd94","tid":683594,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"施斯自始收左皮<br />\n<br />\n踢返都廢哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c0db774741141bd34e1be7aea46d9c1235cd84","tid":683594,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf230a3493c7eb82b32dc862cf2db851593704b","tid":683594,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea135d7efe0eff854d84fa64d7b6fd5b47f3f08","tid":683594,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}